##################
mkimap_server.rb
##################

OLD CODE   - 3 years ago

Remote PostgresSQL server, Cyrus IMAP and Sendmail access through distribute ruby - dRb. 
 It does the following 

    1   creates IMAP accounts
    2.  Sets ACL's on these accounts, 
    3.  Create PostgreSQL User accounts
    4.  Sets up the SENDMAIL config: relay table and mailertable for the new domain
    5.  Update Sendmail config
    6.   Restart Sendmail

    Implements raw Ruby connections to PostgresSQL 
    CRUD for Cyrus IMAP server 
